[25.730695, "o", "\u001b[5S\u001b[5AOn branch main\r\nChanges not staged for commit:\r\n  (use \"git add <file>...\" to update what will be committed)\r\n  (use \"git restore <file>...\" to discard changes in working directory)\u001b[K\u001b[19;8H\u001b[1K\u001b[C\u001b[31mmodified:   README.md\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[K\r\nno changes added to commit (use \"git add\" and/or \"git commit -a\")\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[K"]
